ball.annotation.processing

Interface ClassFileProcessor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Processor
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AntLibProcessor, JAXBIndexProcessor, ManifestProcessor, ServiceProviderForProcessor

    public interface ClassFileProcessor
extends Processor
    Interface to provide an alternate entry point for annotation processing on compiled class files. Implementors must extend AnnotatedProcessor.
    Version:
    $Revision: 7479 $
    Author:
    Allen D. Ball
